# Phase 39C managed local runtime state. By default this lives OUTSIDE the repo
# (under the user's local application-data directory) and is never committed.
# These defensive entries only matter if an operator points HIVEMIND_RUNTIME_HOME
# at a path inside the working tree — runtime metadata and logs stay untracked.
.hivemind-runtime/
runtime-home/
repository-workspaces.json
